request.description:
Get dropdown data for leave request form (employees and leave types). No special permission required.

**Use Case:** Populate dropdowns in leave request form.

**Response:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "employees": [
      {
        "id": "770e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440003",
        "name": "John Doe",
        "email": "john@example.com"
      }
    ],
    "leave_types": [
      {
        "id": "880e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440004",
        "name": "Annual Leave",
        "code": "AL",
        "max_days": 12
      }
    ]
  }
}
```
